According to CEO John Bruce, the idea behind Inrupt is for the company to use resources, processes and skills to make Solid available to everyone.
The company currently includes Berners-Lee, Bruce, some developers hired to work on this project, a community of volunteer programmers, and an IBM-acquired security platform.
